            "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1037750/extras/DemonKing.gif?t=1551189473\" ><br><i>Relive the glory days of being the all-important healer in this single-player, action-adventure!</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intense, real-time action bringing a fresh take on the healer class.<br></li><li>Command a group of 4 warriors through the game's various levels.<br></li><li>Multiple classes to discover, each with unique abilities.<br></li><li>Feel the true struggles of being a healer, with narrative moments inspired by the stories of real doctors.  From the satisfaction of saving a life, to the deep anxiety of a making a medical mistake.  Know the real meaning of being a healer.<br></li><li>Elaborate boss fights designed after MMO raids.<br></li><li>Build and Manage your guild as you decide who joins and who has to leave.  Choose wisely, as your warriors build friendships and rivalries with each other.  Firing a friend can have consequences for those left behind to fight.</li></ul>",
            "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1037750/extras/DemonKing.gif?t=1551189473\" ><br><i>Relive the glory days of being the all-important healer in this single-player, action-adventure!</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intense, real-time action bringing a fresh take on the healer class.<br></li><li>Command a group of 4 warriors through the game's various levels.<br></li><li>Multiple classes to discover, each with unique abilities.<br></li><li>Feel the true struggles of being a healer, with narrative moments inspired by the stories of real doctors.  From the satisfaction of saving a life, to the deep anxiety of a making a medical mistake.  Know the real meaning of being a healer.<br></li><li>Elaborate boss fights designed after MMO raids.<br></li><li>Build and Manage your guild as you decide who joins and who has to leave.  Choose wisely, as your warriors build friendships and rivalries with each other.  Firing a friend can have consequences for those left behind to fight.</li></ul>",
            "short_description": "Command your squad of warriors while keeping them from an early grave in this action-adventure where the healer calls the shots. Heal, shield, and resurrect your way through a world filled with impossible choices, people to save, and elaborate boss fights inspired by MMO dungeon raids.",
